# Aesthetic library attribution + provenance (AUTH2)
# License compliance + attribution integrity — any change must walk the
# license text, provenance, manifest, or NOTICES path, which all have
# downstream obligations (CC-BY-SA-4.0 ShareAlike, BSD-3 attribution).
assets/aesthetic-library/LICENSE.*              @ryanklee
assets/aesthetic-library/_NOTICES.md            @ryanklee
assets/aesthetic-library/_manifest.yaml         @ryanklee
assets/aesthetic-library/**/provenance.yaml     @ryanklee

# Operator anonymity primitives (AUDIT-29 hardening of AUDIT-05)
# Both modules carry single_user / interpersonal_transparency invariants:
# the referent picker is the canonical non-formal-name surface (4
# ratified referents, sticky-per-utterance), and the speech lexicon
# carries pronunciations for those same referents. A regression to
# either silently re-opens the OMG cascade legal-name-leak surface.
shared/operator_referent.py                     @ryanklee
shared/speech_lexicon.py                        @ryanklee
axioms/implications/non-formal-referent-policy.yaml  @ryanklee
